README

Both applications run on all image files within current folder.

Transparancy:

Expects .bmp images in folder 
	- Converts all pixels of given color to Transparent
	
TileMerge:

Expects .png images in folder
	- Merges all png's into one tilesheet (tileSheet.png) in folder (c:\output)
	- Also creates meta file with numbers per tile ( tileSheet_meta.png ) 
		This can be used as a reference 